728145f-c.text:
Van Wyck Boulevard, west side, between Eighty-ninth and Ninety-first Aves., Showing in a set of three view the S. Hasdlett house of 1860.  J.H. Prentice was the owner 1873 to 1891.  In 1842 Jane Such conducted a select school for girls in this house.

1922.
Views 1 and 2.
View 3: April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
